review_blob: Had this in home to celebrate 2 births. A great beer to sub in for Champagne. Golden straw color and very subtle head. The bubbles hang around too. Fresh on the palate.
A very intense flavoured beer. Complex and inky! This was my dessert!

The only one of its kind - this brew - is wheat based (like all the beer they have) and it was great, nice rich dark brown colour, lighter than expected and really nice balance throughout. Id pair this with dark chocolate or tapas!
I love this beer, its a go to Stout - if you havent tried it you are failing yourself.
